    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287970/extras/3b9f711c92d3eb407c630c3519dd735c.avif?t=1749033767\" width=616 height=72 /></span>混沌女神将你转生为了异世界的恶魔领主，而你的任务是带领混沌势力战胜秩序势力。虽然最初的魔王军只有几个哥布林，但你可以通过招募盟友（例如食人魔和恶魔）来将魔王军做强做大。在保卫你的据点——地下城时，你将会遇到各种各样的女性英雄。你可以抓捕她们，“说服”她们加入，并为你保卫地下城！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287970/extras/7b385a367c7224ab9716ca2ed0c4df89.avif?t=1749033767\" width=616 height=72 /></span>从入侵者手中守卫地下城。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将地下城搭建成更坚固的堡垒，并获得更强大的士兵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为”英雄训练师“，捕获、诱降并训练女英雄，让她们成为你的战力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287970/extras/e74ac228aa99d726a5b59c3410baed63.avif?t=1749033767\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287970/extras/59c0a01cc41d8734af7d16243d614c77.avif?t=1749033767\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287970/extras/2c615ea431e7dbe56764d47d576714c8.avif?t=1749033767\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287970/extras/aea79426d89b29ce987fcc9cec425d68.avif?t=1749033767\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287970/extras/f83a7e35f599d9e52a3ef03dfe198e55.avif?t=1749033767\" width=616 height=274 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287970/extras/06ba0c9ff893ba29c5489ab4a548c83d.avif?t=1749033767\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>战略性地下城防御RPG</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过战略规划和谨慎的战力部署来保卫地下城。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不同难度</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在简单模式中享受故事主线，或在地狱模式中测试你的勇气——各有所好。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多个女主</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内含大量不同女主，在满足一定条件后，甚至可以更改她们的着装。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DLC全开</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中已加入包括额外女英雄在内的所有DLC内容。</p>",
